        <abstract>
            <para>The Wildlife Information Centre (TWIC) conducts various excursions to sites across SE/central Scotland in order to collect Biodiversity data. We are helped by many volunteers and expert recorders in this endeavour. This dataset includes data collected by Lothians Wildlife Information Centre (LWIC) from 1995-2009, Scottish Borders Biological Records Centre (SBBRC) Recorders Group up to 2009 and TWIC from 2009 to the present day. Various species groups are recorded, with a special emphasis on vascular plants.</para>
        </abstract>
        <additionalInfo>
            <para>Recorder names have been withheld</para>
        </additionalInfo>
